        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>sourdough pitta[s] </strong>into small pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with enough<strong> olive oil</strong> to cover the base</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>pitta</strong> <strong>chips</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once golden, add your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and <strong>pine kernel & seed mix </strong>to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, transfer the <strong>crispy pitta pieces</strong> and<strong> toasted seeds</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>garlic & herb pitta crunch</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat your <strong>RE:NOURISH broccoli soup </strong>according to the pack instructions</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-broccoli-soup-with-cheesy-garlic-and-herb-pitta-chips/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>heated RE:NOURISH broccoli soup </strong>and top with the <strong>garlic & herb pitta crunch</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
